Let me tell you a story.

Now this is a story all about the Black Nazarene. The Black Nazarene wasn't always black. It used to be just like any other depiction of Jesus Christ carrying a cross. Now this Good Guy Priest comes in and kisses the foot of the saint everyday and all was well.

Then there was this Filthy McRottenDude who hated the priest. One day the dude was about to get it on. He laced poison the the foot of the Nazarene knowing the priest's mannerisms. The Nazarene, concerned about the well being of the priest, absorbed the all of the poison and turned black. And thus came about the Black Nazarene.

The End.
